                <h1>Academic Council examines master&#039;s degree programs in Thursday meeting</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/a06babb3-0a95-44be-a7a4-7defa3b89b06.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;The&#x20;Academic&#x20;Council&#x20;debated&#x20;changes&#x20;to&#x20;the&amp;nbsp&#x3B;ways&#x20;that&#x20;master&#x27;s&#x20;degree&#x20;programs&amp;nbsp&#x3B;can&#x20;be&#x20;approved&#x20;and&#x20;reviewed.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>The Academic Council debated changes to the&nbsp;ways that master's degree programs&nbsp;can be approved and reviewed.</p>

